  <data key="d1">textbook</data>
  <data key="d2">Introduction to Information Retrieval is an optional textbook for CSCE 670, authored by Christopher D. Manning, Prabhakar Raghavan, and Hinrich Schutze, published in 2009, and available online.</data>
