<node id="CSCE 670 Grading Scale">
  <data key="d0">CSCE 670 Grading Scale</data>
  <data key="d1">gradecomponent</data>
  <data key="d2">The grading scale for CSCE 670 defines letter grades based on percentage ranges: A (&gt;=90%), B (&gt;=80% and &lt; 90%), C (&gt;=70% and &lt; 80%), D (&gt;=60% and &lt; 70%).</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-97b761a3d4ccc38fabdc762f72330b3b</data>
